Step 3: Log Analysis Skills (Very Important)

Learn to analyze:

Windows Logs: Security, System, Event ID (4624, 4625)

Linux Logs: /var/log/auth.log, /var/log/syslog

Firewall logs: allow/deny, source/destination IP


üëâ Practice with:

Splunk free

Microsoft Sentinel labs

TryHackMe (SOC paths)



